headline: Wynn Resorts Bolsters Investor Relations Team
summary: LAS VEGAS, December 11, 2024--Wynn Resorts, Limited (NASDAQ: WYNN) ("Wynn Resorts" or the "Company") today announced additions to its investor relations team, deepening the Company’s focus on this important function.
